<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.7">
<l>kārkoḷ vēṅkaikaḷ kaṉavarai taḻuviya</l>
<l>kaṟivaḷark koṭituṉṉi</l>
<l>pōrkoḷ vēṅkaikaḷ puṉavarai taḻuviya</l>
<l>pūmpoḻi limayattuḷ</l>
<l>ērkoḷ pūñcuṉait taṭampaṭin tiṉamala</l>
<l>reṭṭumiṭ ṭimaiyōrkaḷ</l>
<l>pērka ḷāyiram paraviniṉ ṟaṭitoḻum</l>
<l>piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the Himalaya where in flourishing groves vēnkai [tigers], fit for battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">embrace [in combat] on dry hills,</l>
<l>Being entangled in the pepper-growing creepers</l>
<l rend="indent">which embrace low hills of cloud-enveloped vēṅkai [trees],</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti, where the unblinking [celestials],</l>
<l rend="indent">plunging in beautiful, flourishing spring pools,</l>
<l>Placing eight varieties of flowers, worship [his] feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">continually reciting [his] one-thousand names.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
